00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:10,600
Xiaoxiao.

98
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:12,440
Xiaoxiao.

99
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:24,920
Xuanxuan.

100
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:27,800
I'm going to Korea for a few days

101
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,600
to handle the hospital records.

102
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:32,159
Be extra careful these days.

103
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,200
If anything happens,

104
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,120
