105
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:36,799
Xiaoxiao.

106
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,200
Are you sick?

107
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:41,210
Why is your voice so hoarse?

108
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:43,039
It's nothing.

109
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:43,900
Just a cold.

110
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:52,120
How could this be?

111
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:53,880
How is that possible?

112
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:57,360
How could I?

113
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:58,920
Having a face

114
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:02,090
that looks exactly like yours, right?

115
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:13,460
Who are you really?

116
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:15,920
Xuanxuan.

117
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:20,170
