118
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,400
This is my home.

119
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:25,520
You're Xiaoxiao.

120
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:35,280
Xiaoxiao.

121
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:37,400
