133
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,680
I had no choice but to sneak into Korea.

134
00:10:09,680 --> 00:10:10,940
To become another you.

135
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:12,880
I couldn't take that chance.

136
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,660
I won't let you bear

137
00:10:14,760 --> 00:10:16,120
