138
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,000
You know what?

139
00:10:18,160 --> 00:10:18,640
No.

140
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:24,860
It shouldn't be like this.

141
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:26,980
How did it come to this?

142
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:29,920
Xuanxuan.

143
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:32,520
From now on,

144
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,720
