148
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,800
he will propose to you.

149
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,040
What?

150
00:10:57,800 --> 00:10:58,520
Propose?

151
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:01,080
You can only legally inherit his property

152
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:02,080
if you marry him

153
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:04,600
and after his death.

154
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,080
Shelly.

155
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:20,640
Since Xie Yuxuan is missing

156
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:23,410
and Xiangyang has issues with Leng Xiaoxiao,

157
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,680
you're my only

158
00:11:27,520 --> 00:11:28,880
breakthrough now.

159
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:30,960
Zhiqiu.

160
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,200
Surprise.

161
00:11:34,280 --> 00:11:35,000
Shelly,

162
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:37,160
what brings you here?

163
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:38,600
I came to see you.

164
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:46,520
A celebrity's life

165
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:49,170
is indeed different from ordinary people's.

166
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,360
Such a big house.

167
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:54,400
I could never afford it in my lifetime.

168
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:55,530
Please, have a seat.

169
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:57,800
Shelly.

170
00:11:58,840 --> 00:11:59,840
It's been a while.

171
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:02,620
It's been a long time since we talked.

172
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:03,760
How have you been?

173
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:07,800
It hasn't been that long.

174
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:11,450
Didn't you contact me a few months ago?

175
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,890
I didn't even ask what it was about.

176
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:14,760
Right.

177
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,400
I completely forgot.

178
00:12:18,560 --> 00:12:20,890
The privileged sure have short memories.

179
00:12:21,040 --> 00:12:21,600
What?

180
00:12:22,160 --> 00:12:23,720
Found yourself a rich husband

181
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,520
and rushed to quit the industry.

182
00:12:25,800 --> 00:12:28,040
Moving up the social ladder quickly, aren't you?

183
00:12:28,040 --> 00:12:29,440
Can't be envious of that.

184
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:33,200
There's no such thing as crossing class barriers.

185
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,860
It's nothing special anyway.

186
00:12:35,040 --> 00:12:36,680
This lack of confidence...

187
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:40,080
Is this really our big star Ye Zhiqiu?

188
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:43,000
Why do I feel like

189
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:45,000
you're much more approachable

190
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:47,720
than you appear on the big screen?

191
00:12:50,880 --> 00:12:52,120
In movies,

192
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:54,010
I'm always wearing makeup.

193
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:58,210
Aren't you curious?

194
00:13:00,400 --> 00:13:02,240
How I managed to find your home?

195
00:13:04,200 --> 00:13:06,060
What's there to be curious about?

196
00:13:06,640 --> 00:13:07,600
We have

197
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:09,680
so many mutual friends.

198
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:13,340
You couldn't have asked Xiangyang about it, right?

199
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:17,040
Although his office building

200
00:13:18,560 --> 00:13:20,080
is quite eye-catching.

201
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:22,480
I know my boundaries.

202
00:13:23,400 --> 00:13:24,930
Xiangyang is your husband.

203
00:13:25,560 --> 00:13:27,620
How could I go to him behind your back?

204
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:29,160
Besides,

205
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:31,480
We were roommates in college.

206
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:34,680
Shouldn't I come to you first when I need something?

207
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:35,940
I can't just bypass you

208
00:13:36,280 --> 00:13:38,280
and go straight to your sugar daddy.

209
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:41,040
Shelly.

210
00:13:41,560 --> 00:13:43,560
Do you need something from me?

211
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:47,280
Nothing.

212
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:50,280
I just missed my old classmate

213
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:51,720
and wanted to drop by.

214
00:13:54,680 --> 00:13:56,240
We should hang out more often.

215
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:56,800
Sure.

216
00:13:58,960 --> 00:14:00,400
Please, have a seat anywhere.

217
00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:01,320
Two flatbreads.

218
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:01,980
No, thanks.

219
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:05,540
You're Ye Zhiqiu's agent.

220
00:14:10,400 --> 00:14:11,480
Former agent.

221
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:13,770
What do you want from me?

222
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:16,600
Do you still keep in touch with your college roommates:

223
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:18,930
Ye Zhiqiu, Leng Xiaoxiao, and Xie Yuxuan?

224
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:20,740
Any contact with them?

225
00:14:22,280 --> 00:14:23,210
Two flatbreads.

226
00:14:23,760 --> 00:14:24,890
You came all this way

227
00:14:25,160 --> 00:14:27,360
just to dig up ancient history?

228
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:29,720
This is important.

229
00:14:30,640 --> 00:14:31,560
Recently,

230
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:33,650
we held a press conference.

231
00:14:34,160 --> 00:14:36,090
Ye Zhiqiu is retiring from acting.

232
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:38,000
At the press conference,

233
00:14:38,040 --> 00:14:39,160
we caused quite a stir.

234
00:14:39,160 --> 00:14:41,360
Although Xiangyang later paid off the media

235
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:42,420
to keep them quiet,

236
00:14:42,480 --> 00:14:44,240
some information still leaked out.

237
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:45,000
Alright.

238
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:48,130
You came to me asking about these old stories,

239
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:52,000
so I need to know what's in it for me.

240
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:55,560
I don't do business at a loss.

241
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:00,160
Fine.

242
00:15:01,360 --> 00:15:03,920
