247
00:15:17,920 --> 00:15:18,800
As for housing,

248
00:15:21,040 --> 00:15:22,500
I do want to get a new place.

249
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:25,320
Ye Zhiqiu.

250
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:28,880
She did contact me recently.

251
00:15:29,880 --> 00:15:30,680
Shelly.

252
00:15:31,800 --> 00:15:34,360
I see you've lost so much weight.

253
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,480
Are you not feeling well?

254
00:15:39,400 --> 00:15:40,860
This is called being lean.

255
00:15:40,960 --> 00:15:44,090
All that money spent at the gym has to show for something.

256
00:15:44,160 --> 00:15:45,490
Watch out for this girl.

257
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:47,520
She's no pushover.

258
00:15:48,160 --> 00:15:48,760
Back then,

259
00:15:49,400 --> 00:15:51,120
she was always causing trouble.

260
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:52,450
Going to the gym is good.

261
00:15:52,480 --> 00:15:54,920
Health is the most important thing now.

262
00:15:58,680 --> 00:16:00,840
Back in the day, you and I were fine.

263
00:16:01,160 --> 00:16:02,220
But Leng Xiaoxiao,

264
00:16:02,560 --> 00:16:04,220
she was always picking on you.

265
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:06,130
But you never held a grudge.

266
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:09,810
Are you still in touch with her?

267
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:11,980
Finally getting to the point.

268
00:16:12,680 --> 00:16:13,540
Leng Xiaoxiao?

269
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:16,640
We haven't been in touch for many years.

270
00:16:17,520 --> 00:16:18,280
Really?

271
00:16:19,960 --> 00:16:22,160
I'd really like to get in touch with her.

272
00:16:23,560 --> 00:16:25,560
Why don't we get together sometime?

273
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:29,040
I don't even have her contact information anymore.

274
00:16:29,040 --> 00:16:30,400
How can we meet up?

275
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:32,980
What about Xie Yuxuan?

276
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:35,300
Wasn't she close with Leng Xiaoxiao?

277
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:36,850
Have you seen her recently?

278
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:42,920
I heard her husband died.

279
00:16:44,120 --> 00:16:45,520
That hopeless romantic,

280
00:16:45,840 --> 00:16:47,520
who knows if she'll remarry.

281
00:16:51,480 --> 00:16:52,160
Really?

282
00:16:55,160 --> 00:16:56,400
Xie Yuxuan.

283
00:16:56,800 --> 00:16:58,960
We haven't been in touch for a long time.

284
00:16:58,960 --> 00:17:00,820
I'm not sure about her situation.

285
00:17:04,280 --> 00:17:06,119
Look at your memory.

286
00:17:07,839 --> 00:17:10,040
How could you pretend not to know

287
00:17:10,119 --> 00:17:12,319
your roommate of four years in college?

288
00:17:13,560 --> 00:17:14,440
